      Sets the Round based on difficulty and what round it currently is.
      Parameters:
      _roundDifficulty - The requested difficulty of the game.
      treeCarts - the number of tree carts in the round
      rockCarts - the number of stone carts in the round
      fruitCarts - the number of fruit carts in the round
      _activeTowers - List of all current towers in the game.
      _anchorPane - Anchor pane to attach the cart image to.
      _startButton - Button that starts the round.
      _shopButton - Button that opens the shop.

      _rm - Round manager with all the relevant info for the round.
